Traverso ( Multitrack DAW )

Traverso is an audio recording and editing program which is very well suited to record a single voice, a band, an ensemble, a whole orchestra or any other source of music.

Homepage: http://traverso-daw.org

Deps:

Jack support: libjack
liblame (Optional for MP3 write support) (Seems broken for now)
raptor2

For LV2 support the stock redland and rasqal packages need upgrading so this option is turned off currently.
